OL,3,CProgramme listings for TUE 5 MAY
OL,4,G0055FDynasties II
OL,5,     GIn the wild Patagonian mountains,
OL,6,     Ga puma battles to raise her
OL,7,     Gbiggest litter yet.
OL,8,G0155FThe Green Planet
OL,9,     GTropical rainforests are plant
OL,10,     Gbattlegrounds. New filming
OL,11,     Gtechniques allow us to enter the
OL,12,     Gworld of plants to see it from
OL,13,     Gtheir perspective and on their
OL,14,     Gtimescale.
OL,15,G0255FMammals
OL,16,     GThe dark, a world of opportunity
OL,17,     Gfor mammals. More than two-thirds
OL,18,     Gprefer the cover of the night,
OL,19,     Gwith some now returning to the
OL,20,     Gsafety of the shadows in order to
OL,21,     Gavoid us.
OL,22,G0355FThis is BBC Three
